    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I did so because, in the then state of the Labour party, had they succeeded in passing their Motion we should have been more defenceless in a war even than we were in September, 1939.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-19bac2c2-363e-4abf-b6c0-2f8c3c98d4cc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
